  "title": "Manage Data on Your Atlas Cluster Using AWS AppSync Lambda Resolvers",
  "description": "You can manage data on your Atlas cluster using AWS (Amazon Web Services) AppSync Direct\nLambda Resolvers. The Lambda function, serving as a resolver for the AWS (Amazon Web Services)\nAppSync GraphQL API, enables seamless\nCRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations on your data in\nyour Atlas cluster. Integrating Atlas with AWS (Amazon Web Services) AppSync offers\na powerful, flexible solution for building scalable, serverless GraphQL\nAPIs.",
